# SIXMEN QA

## Memory Scope

This rule must keep active:

- **Scope governed:** Pest tests, ERP safety matrix, permission/concurrency/inventory consistency checks.
- **Canonical context:** `sixmen-qa.mdc` · `docs/erp/core/04_Architecture.md` §13 · `.cursor/templates/sixmen/architecture-tests-skeleton.md` · `docs/ai-agent/reference/phase-gates.md` Gate 1→2.
- **Required project memory:** 403 mọi protected mutation · document number concurrency · movement+balance same tx · no `pgsql_reporting` mutation · CTY/HKD scope · P0 fail blocks release.
- **Deprecated / rejected:** test scaffold cho mọi CRUD service như critical guard · skip 403 vì “UI đã ẩn”.
- **Applies to:** `tests/**`, `**/*Test.php`, sau implement / trước release.
- **Does not apply to:** docs-only (trừ AC review); domain không đụng stock/docs → không bắt full guard matrix.
- **Conflict handling:** data-safety + envelope define what to test; governance gate nếu release thiếu approval.
- **Stop condition:** risky change (schema/stock/permission) thiếu test plan · P0 fail mà vẫn release · env thiếu chạy security test.

## Purpose

Test case, edge case, regression, permission/security — catch ERP-specific failures.

## Use when

- After backend/frontend implement
- Before release
- PR architecture compliance review

## Required inputs

- `task-brief.md` DoD
- `acceptance-criteria.md` (if business feature)
- Changed modules / permissions

## Framework

Pest PHP — `tests/Feature/`, `tests/Unit/`

## Critical domain guard tests

> Chỉ khi backend đụng stock, documents, COGS, hoặc mutation critical — **không** yêu cầu test mọi CRUD service.

When backend touches stock, documents, COGS, or mutations:

- [ ] No direct `inventory` update outside `InventoryService`
- [ ] No direct `material_inventory_balances` update outside `MaterialInventoryService`
- [ ] Document number concurrency — no duplicate (`FOR UPDATE` + transaction)
- [ ] Inventory/material: movement + balance consistent (same transaction)
- [ ] Mutation services do **not** use `pgsql_reporting`
- [ ] Movement/audit not updated/deleted to fix business mistakes

## Required ERP safety tests

> Phần Critical domain guard tests ở trên — tick khi domain đụng tới; không duplicate scaffold cho CRUD thường.

For backend/migration features, cover:

- [ ] `migrate:fresh --seed` passes
- [ ] Unauthorized user → **403**
- [ ] Invalid input → **422** (API/FormRequest)
- [ ] IDOR / scope: CTY vs HKD isolation
- [ ] `super_admin` bypass still audited
- [ ] Document number: no duplicate under concurrency (`FOR UPDATE` + transaction)
- [ ] Inventory: movement + balance consistent (same transaction)
- [ ] Material inventory: movement + balance consistent
- [ ] Soft delete hides default UI; no hard delete of referenced records
- [ ] Mutation services do **not** use `pgsql_reporting`
- [ ] No direct `inventory` / `material_inventory_balances` update outside Service

## GĐ1 regression (bổ sung)

- GRN TC-PUR-01 · LSX TC-PROD-03/08
- Login, audit log, Shield sync
- PR: `architecture-compliance-checklist.md`

## Post-feature review gate *(sau xong 1 tính năng — trước PR/review)*

1. **Detect:** `codacy.mdc` trên file PHP/JS đã sửa; Trivy nếu đổi dependency; `pint` / `phpstan` / `pest` khi có repo
2. **Verify:** tick `architecture-compliance-checklist.md` + ERP safety tests (§ trên)
3. **Report:** `test-plan.md` — P0 fail → block review

Codacy không có → log fallback; vẫn bắt checklist + Pest P0.

**Artifacts:** ghi `artifacts/{Task-ID}/06-test-plan.md` · `07-architecture-compliance-checklist.md` · cập nhật `00-gate-status.md` (`qa_gate`). Thiếu → **review blocker**.

## Output contract

- Test cases (Given/When/Then or Pest descriptions)
- Pest files added/updated
- Manual regression checklist
- Pass/fail per case
- Blockers
- Risks not tested

Template: `.cursor/templates/sixmen/test-plan.md`

## Final checklist

- [ ] 403 for every protected mutation
- [ ] Concurrency test for document numbers (if applicable)
- [ ] Inventory consistency (if stock touched)
- [ ] P0 fail → block release
